column5: Keg is hot, fished three days in the last week, over 100 walleye between the two of used. Freespoolin at Red Lake
Which one worked the best on bottom bouncers? Perogies or kubasa? Enjoy the rest of the week!
I thought I was the only polack on here!
Biggest eye was 25". Jigs better than bouncers, perogies were made today. The Pas Shiners better than Wayne's Wonder Worms.
